text:
I can't speak highly enough or express my relief after finding Taylor on Airtasker!
There's not many things you CAN'T request help with on this awesome APP and will certainly be using it again and again!
No more worries on how I'm going to get something done as a quick posting of a task can get dozens of ireplies of people 'ready and able' to get it done!!
THANK YOU AIRTASKER, you've solved a multitude of problems!! üëç
